{{define "title"}}Tags - Wallpapers{{end}}

{{define "content"}}
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Tags</h2>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">{{len .Tags}} unique tags extracted from wallpapers. More common tags appear larger.</p>

<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4 leading-relaxed items-baseline">
  {{range .Tags}}
  <a href="/?q={{.Word}}" class="badge badge-outline gap-1 no-underline">
    {{.Word}}<span class="text-gray-400 text-xs ml-0.5">{{.Count}}</span>
  </a>
  {{end}}
</div>
{{end}}
